stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> submitted: 作者投稿

    submitted --> me_precheck: 进入入口审查
    me_precheck --> returned_to_author: 技术审查不通过
    returned_to_author --> submitted: 作者修改后重投

    me_precheck --> ae_assigned: 技术审查通过
    ae_assigned --> academic_precheck: ME 分配 AE 后提交学术初审
    academic_precheck --> rejected: 学术初审拒稿
    academic_precheck --> under_review: 学术初审通过

    under_review --> decision: 报告达标后 AE 汇总

    decision --> revision_minor: 小修
    revision_minor --> resubmitted_minor: 作者修回
    resubmitted_minor --> decision: AE 核查后再次决策

    decision --> revision_major: 大修
    revision_major --> resubmitted_major: 作者修回
    resubmitted_major --> under_review: 必须二审

    decision --> approved: 接收
    decision --> rejected: 拒稿

    approved --> proofing: 生产排版与校对
    approved --> invoiced: 财务开票

    proofing --> ready_for_publish: 校对完成
    invoiced --> paid: 财务确认到账

    ready_for_publish --> published: 与 Paid 同时满足门禁
    paid --> published: 与 Ready 同时满足门禁

    published --> [*]
    rejected --> [*]
